ASUS RT-AX57 AX3000 3000mbps Dual Band WiFi 6 Gaming Router
The ASUS RT-AX57 AX3000 Wireless Dual-Band Gigabit Router is designed to provide smooth 4K video streaming, online gaming, and internet browsing experiences for your home network. With Wi-Fi 6 (802.11ax) technology, ASUS RT-AX57 AX3000 Dual Band WiFi 6 Router offers long-reaching coverage and can transfer up to 2976 Mb/s over the 2.4 and 5 GHz bands with compatible devices. It is powered by a 1.7 GHz quad-core processor with four external antennas, which can transfer up to 2402 Mb/s on the 5 GHz band and 574 Mb/s over the 2.4 GHz frequency. ASUS RT-AX57 AX3000 Dual Band WiFi 6 Router also offers BSS Coloring technology to improve Wi-Fi connection efficiency with compatible devices, even in crowded environments. ASUS RT-AX57 AX3000 Dual Band WiFi 6 Router comes with four Gigabit Ethernet LAN ports for wired devices and AiProtection Classic features for added security. The ASUS Router App allows for easy management and setup from your iOS or Android device, and AiMesh Compatibility allows you to expand your Wi-Fi coverage with any ASUS AiMesh compatible router as a mesh network satellite. The Instant Guard VPN technology provides safe internet access through your home network while using public Wi-Fi.

name: ASUS RT-AX52 AX1800 Dual Band WiFi Router
brandDescription: This is the global brand
description:
Asus RT-AX52 AX1800 1800mbps Dual Band Gigabit Wi-Fi 6 AiMesh Router
The Asus RT-AX52 AX1800 Dual Band Gigabit WiFi 6 AiMesh Router is a cutting-edge networking solution that delivers ultra-fast, dependable, and efficient wireless connectivity to your home or workplace. The RT-AX52, which uses the newest 802.11ax WiFi 6 standard, outperforms prior versions in terms of performance and efficiency. With a total networking speed of up to 1800 Mbps, it provides 574 Mbps on the 2.4GHz band and an astonishing 1201 Mbps on the 5GHz band, guaranteeing fast internet access for all of your devices. The RT-AX52 AX1800 has innovative technologies such as 1024-QAM (Quadrature Amplitude Modulation), which greatly improves wireless connection rates for demanding applications like streaming, gaming, and huge file transfers. It supports the MU-MIMO (Multi-User, Multiple Input, Multiple Output) and OFDMA (Orthogonal Frequency Division Multiple Access) protocols. MU-MIMO enables the router to connect with numerous devices at the same time, whereas OFDMA optimizes channel allocation to reduce latency and improve overall network efficiency. The RT-AX52 AX1800 works with AiMesh-compatible routers to provide expanded coverage and smooth connectivity across your house, allowing you to build a full mesh network with sophisticated capabilities. This provides a continuous and strong WiFi connection in every area of your home. The Asus RT-AX52 AX1800 provides a cutting-edge WiFi experience with fast speeds, efficient technologies, and easy network extension features. It is an excellent solution for anyone looking to enhance their home or office network to the highest levels of speed and performance.
